VOCATIONAL GUIDANCE' THE SEARCH AND THE PROBLEMS.
     
GRYUB RSFSR IMENI 50-LETIYA VLKSM, (RSFSR 50TH KOMSOMOL JUBILEE STATE REPUBLIC
YOUTH LIBRARY), (SRYL), RECEIVES MANY ENQUIRIES ABOUT CAREERS. LIBRARY LIAISON
WITH SCHOOLS IS ESSENTIAL. SRYL INVESTIGATED THE RELATIONSHIP OF READING WITH
COGNITIVE INTERESTS AND PROFESSIONAL ASPIRATIONS OF 8TH-10TH FORMERS. 27.5% OF
8TH-FORMERS, 26.4% OF 9TH-FORMERS AND 42.6% OF 10TH-FORMERS HAD CHOSEN THEIR
PROFESSION. TEACHERS AND LIBRARIANS PROVE INADEQUATE INFORMATION SOURCES OWING
TO IGNORANCE OF THE LITERATURE. TO HELP LIBRARIANS SRYL HAS PREPARED A
BIBLIOGRAPHY' 2ALL ABOUT JOBS. 1SRYL PLANS AN EXPERIMENT' JOINT LIBRARY AND
SCHOOL WORK ON VOCATIONAL GUIDANCE FOR SENIOR PUPILS.
